  "description": "Group envelope rate at 0.88 — near the edge of audio-rate modulation. At this speed the group envelope becomes a rhythmic artifact rather than a smooth swell. Voices stutter and surge in irregular patterns. A Lagrange point is a gravitational equilibrium that is inherently unstable. This is that.",
